      "widgets_values": [
        "{\"version\":1,\"content\":\"<h1><span data-ic=\\\"workflow-v1\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;Models &amp; Nodes Used in This Workflow</h1>\\n\\n<p>This workflow uses <b>Z-Image Turbo</b> (GGUF) with a <b>Qwen-4B</b> text encoder and the <b>Flux VAE</b>. Download all three below — each goes into a different ComfyUI folder.</p>\\n\\n<hr>\\n\\n<h2><span data-ic=\\\"GGUF\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" style=\\\"color: #b565e2\\\"></span>&nbsp;Unet Loader (GGUF)</h2>\\n\\n<p>Main diffusion model. <b>Create the <code>z-image</code> folder inside <code>diffusion_models</code> if it doesn't exist.</b></p>\\n\\n<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnblock\\\"><a class=\\\"pix-note-dl\\\" href=\\\"https://huggingface.co/gguf-org/z-image-gguf/resolve/main/z-image-turbo-q4_k_s.gguf?download=true\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">z-image-turbo-q4_k_s.gguf<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnsize\\\">~1.5 GB</span></a><span class=\\\"pix-note-folderhint\\\">Place in: ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models/z-image</span></span>&nbsp;\\n\\n<p><span data-ic=\\\"puzzle\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" style=\\\"color: #888888\\\"></span>&nbsp;More quant options: <a href=\\\"https://huggingface.co/gguf-org/z-image-gguf/tree/main\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">z-image-gguf on HuggingFace</a></p>\\n\\n<hr>\\n\\n<h2><span data-ic=\\\"CLIP\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" style=\\\"color: #00bcd4\\\"></span>&nbsp;CLIPLoader (GGUF)</h2>\\n\\n<p>Text encoder — converts your prompt into embeddings for the diffusion model.</p>\\n\\n<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnblock\\\"><a class=\\\"pix-note-dl\\\" href=\\\"https://huggingface.co/Lockout/qwen3-4b-heretic-zimage/resolve/main/qwen-4b-zimage-heretic-q8.gguf?download=true\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">qwen-4b-zimage-heretic-q8.gguf<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnsize\\\">~4 GB</span></a><span class=\\\"pix-note-folderhint\\\">Place in: ComfyUI/models/text_encoders</span></span>&nbsp;\\n\\n<hr>\\n\\n<h2><span data-ic=\\\"VAE\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" style=\\\"color: #5bd45b\\\"></span>&nbsp;Load VAE</h2>\\n\\n<p>Flux 1 VAE — decodes the model's latent output back into pixels.</p>\\n\\n<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnblock\\\"><a class=\\\"pix-note-dl\\\" href=\\\"https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/z_image_turbo/resolve/main/split_files/vae/ae.safetensors\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">ae.safetensors<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnsize\\\">335 MB</span></a><span class=\\\"pix-note-folderhint\\\">Place in: ComfyUI/models/vae</span></span>&nbsp;\\n\\n<hr>\\n\\n<p><span data-ic=\\\"warning-v1\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" style=\\\"color: #f1c40f\\\"></span>&nbsp;<b>Tip:</b> Each pill opens the download page in a new tab. The folder path under each pill tells you where to save the file.</p>\",\"buttonColor\":\"#f66744\",\"lineColor\":\"#f66744\",\"width\":400,\"height\":200}",
