        "{\"version\":1,\"content\":\"<h2><span data-ic=\\\"pixaroma\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;Pixaroma Community</h2><p>\\n\\n</p><p>Tutorials, workflows, and updates from the Pixaroma team. Everything lives in one place — pick your favourite:</p><p>\\n\\n</p><h3>Connect</h3><p>\\n\\n</p><p><a class=\\\"pix-note-yt\\\" href=\\\"https://www.youtube.com/@pixaroma\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">Subscribe on YouTube</a>&nbsp;<a class=\\\"pix-note-discord\\\" href=\\\"https://discord.com/invite/gggpkVgBf3\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">Join the Discord</a></p><p>\\n\\n</p><h3>Resources</h3><p>\\n\\n<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnblock\\\"><a class=\\\"pix-note-rm\\\" href=\\\"https://github.com/pixaroma/ComfyUI-Pixaroma\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">GitHub Repository</a></span>&nbsp;\\n\\n<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnblock\\\"><a class=\\\"pix-note-vp\\\" href=\\\"https://huggingface.co/pixaroma\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">HuggingFace Profile</a></span>&nbsp;\\n\\n</p><h3>Quick Links</h3><p>\\n\\n</p><ul>\\n  <li><span data-ic=\\\"github\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" style=\\\"color: #ffffff\\\"></span>&nbsp;<b>Source:</b> <a href=\\\"https://github.com/pixaroma/ComfyUI-Pixaroma\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">github.com/pixaroma</a></li>\\n  <li><span data-ic=\\\"huggingface\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" style=\\\"color: #f1c40f\\\"></span>&nbsp;<b>Models:</b> <a href=\\\"https://huggingface.co/pixaroma\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">huggingface.co/pixaroma</a></li>\\n  <li><span data-ic=\\\"question\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" style=\\\"color: #00bcd4\\\"></span>&nbsp;<b>Help:</b> open an <a href=\\\"https://github.com/pixaroma/ComfyUI-Pixaroma/issues\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">issue on GitHub</a></li>\\n</ul><p>\\n\\n</p><hr><p>\\n