        "{\"version\":1,\"content\":\"<h3><span data-ic=\\\"warning-v1\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" style=\\\"color: #f1c40f\\\"></span>&nbsp;VRAM Requirement</h3><p>\\n</p><p>This workflow needs at least <b>8 GB VRAM</b>. If you hit out-of-memory errors, try lowering the batch size or switching to a smaller quant (Q4 instead of Q8).</p>\",\"buttonColor\":\"#f66744\",\"lineColor\":\"#f66744\",\"width\":350.30944165039045,\"height\":141.43599999999992,\"backgroundColor\":\"#b91f0e\"}",
