      "widgets_values": [
        "{\"version\":1,\"content\":\"<h1><span data-ic=\\\"workflow-v1\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;SDXL Workflow Guide</h1><p>\\n\\n</p><p>This workflow produces <b>high-detail</b> 1024×1024 images in <i>~20 seconds</i> on a modern GPU. Tweak the highlighted values to experiment:</p><p>\\n\\n</p><p><span style=\\\"background-color: #f1c40f; color: #111111\\\">&nbsp;CFG 7.5&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;<span style=\\\"background-color: #5bd45b; color: #111111\\\">&nbsp;Steps 30&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;<span style=\\\"background-color: #b565e2; color: #ffffff\\\">&nbsp;Sampler dpmpp_2m&nbsp;</span></p><p>\\n\\n</p><h2><span data-ic=\\\"gear\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;Settings</h2><p>\\n\\n</p><table class=\\\"pix-note-grid\\\">\\n  <thead>\\n    <tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Value</th><th>Range</th></tr>\\n  </thead>\\n  <tbody>\\n    <tr><td>CFG</td><td>7.5</td><td>4 – 12</td></tr>\\n    <tr><td>Steps</td><td>30</td><td>20 – 50</td></tr>\\n    <tr><td>Seed</td><td>random</td><td>any int</td></tr>\\n    <tr><td>Resolution</td><td>1024 × 1024</td><td>SDXL native</td></tr>\\n  </tbody>\\n</table><p>\\n\\n</p><h3><span data-ic=\\\"checkmark\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" style=\\\"color: #5bd45b\\\"></span>&nbsp;Steps</h3><p>\\n\\n</p><ol>\\n  <li><span data-ic=\\\"model-v1\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;Load <b>Checkpoint Loader</b> → pick SDXL Base</li>\\n  <li><span data-ic=\\\"chip\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" style=\\\"color: #00bcd4\\\"></span>&nbsp;Write your prompt in <b>CLIP Text Encode</b></li>\\n  <li><span data-ic=\\\"node-v2\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" style=\\\"color: #b565e2\\\"></span>&nbsp;Wire into <b>KSampler</b></li>\\n  <li><span data-ic=\\\"checkmark\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" style=\\\"color: #5bd45b\\\"></span>&nbsp;Run — the image shows up in <b>Save Image</b></li>\\n</ol><p>\\n\\n</p><h3><span data-ic=\\\"file\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;Example Prompt</h3><p>\\n\\n</p><pre><code>masterpiece, cinematic portrait, golden hour,\\nultra detailed, 8k resolution, f/1.8 shallow depth</code></pre><p>\\n\\n</p><hr><p>\\n\\n</p><p style=\\\"text-align: center; color: #888888\\\"><i>Lower CFG (4–6) = more creative. Higher CFG (8–12) = sticks to prompt.</i></p>\",\"buttonColor\":\"#f66744\",\"lineColor\":\"#394551\",\"width\":648.666748046875,\"height\":619.3333129882812,\"backgroundColor\":\"#2e2d34\"}",
